My go to this spring/summer! I highly recommend trying it out!

New @sephoracollection Color twister oil-in-stick in Freaky Fushia ✨☁️🌸

 as soon as I saw this drop I knew I needed to try it! This is such a unique formula containing 90% oils so it literally just melts on the skin. 

I love a multi-use product and this combination of a blush and lip oil is a must! It changes colour once it contacts the skin and the pigment is definitely buildable. 

I highly recommend trying it out!
